00:01:06,710 --> 00:01:08,280
Watching me from heaven.

11
00:01:10,200 --> 00:01:11,120
Miss.

12
00:01:13,480 --> 00:01:15,230
The dead cannot be brought back to life.

13
00:01:17,070 --> 00:01:18,590
The old general must hope that you

14
00:01:18,590 --> 00:01:20,070
take good care of yourself.

15
00:01:25,480 --> 00:01:26,480
Miss.

16
00:01:27,000 --> 00:01:29,510
